cu500 | 1 | Text area measures 13 x 20 cm.  The ornamentation is comparatively simple.  It consists of filling the loops of the letters with gold and the loop of initial &apos;ayn with a gold dot in the center.  8 petaled whirling gold rosettes with blue and red dots mark the ends of verses.  It is impossible to determine the verse count system since this manuscript contains surahs and verses that are counted alike in all the different systems.
